curam.util.ctm.bom

Class BusinessObjectsComparer

  • java.lang.Object
    • curam.util.ctm.bom.MapDataComparer
      • curam.util.ctm.bom.BusinessObjectsComparer

  • public class BusinessObjectsComparer
extends MapDataComparer
    A comparer implementation that compares the content of two business object instances. A business object instance as identified through a BusinessObjectIdentifier will be converted into a raw multiple valued map and then will be provided as an input to this comparer implementation.
